frames.caption: A picturesque rural scene features several wooden cottages nestled in a lush green valley. Cows graze peacefully in the foreground, while a winding dirt path leads through the vibrant landscape. The sky is clear with fluffy white clouds, adding to the serene atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene is set in a tranquil countryside, showcasing a harmonious blend of nature and rustic architecture. Wooden cottages are surrounded by verdant fields and grazing cattle, creating a peaceful rural setting.
